{"id": "98ae1e6811a73e15cb8aca9e380bdfef3cb85159f169e1b4ca87c44581198e93", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:0", "text": "实例适合通过引用一份原始副本来复制几何体；在处理和渲染大量对象时，这可以节省内存和时间。随后可以为这些实例赋予不同着色，生成有趣且真实的变化，而不必让艺术家或计算机承担大量唯一副本的负担。"}
{"id": "6863067eb0a2c7499425c6c189b2c88bac55ca754285a6ab1ef37b75b4cfad4d", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:1", "text": "参见"}
{"id": "c38596ee07aa4afce098935bb04038d8eb8116833380c34c25306ae82961910c", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:2", "text": "Instancing（实例化）"}
{"id": "95c9b975ef8e64878dbfabdf6f911f486df1ee58e719eea815cb699da3dbc0f6", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:3", "text": "了解有关实例化的更多信息。"}
{"id": "c4edc47eaec92810bb49c5b7272e5c2e148b36c28062a50df55dedfcb4f41843", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:4", "text": "Copy to Points SOP（复制到点 SOP）"}
{"id": "a2a769e959cfd33c6744a4099fd4d901e8e2814f5dce4ca3f330aece5991d1ef", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:5", "text": "创建一个"}
{"id": "7c2e012a5760244b5844dfa679e66adfa4371239d3156ec75173a6536e3fec7e", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:6", "text": "Copy to Points"}
{"id": "fae32168683cdaa3b8bf0b1522112d2d17e8e8e01c104e9acc902f34f21cd9cd", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:7", "text": "SOP，将要实例化的几何体连接到第一个输入，并将用于放置实例的位置连接到第二个输入。"}
{"id": "8f9aa35310cfe894e0b75ea6464a7a10b0202a9ec77dc088173187ee52310742", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:8", "text": "Instance OBJ（实例 OBJ）"}
{"id": "50bda0b2ae2e492d449abab3c20306dec8a966893451d9b044cda70a7db59b3d", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:9", "text": "创建一个"}
{"id": "425f233626b3cd02e48954803f450ad165ac9d36d44181cd6ec2f3166573f606", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:10", "text": "Instance"}
{"id": "1f99e0a5abaf7196897f9bb7710cc113b7d2d10bc030e520ba75418bd6dc3d13", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:11", "text": "OBJ，方式与平常创建"}
{"id": "d32e43c44b03f2d9a1ec926cc856008c6d1016e8b3e2ef72d71e6e2f75a2763d", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:12", "text": "Houdini instances（Houdini 实例）"}
{"id": "cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:13", "text": "。"}
{"id": "2e8644ad480f09c612eb5ea9e4d3441c7f5a515be231a930fd0a5523de929fb5", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:14", "text": "在 Instance 节点中，设置"}
{"id": "d16a57517c1f6cf42eadc0846ced9390c7ce937398bdf253aeea671959e27cb6", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:15", "text": "Instance object（实例对象）"}
{"id": "ea7fdc00423772003dda75272b78b41048611d650c6ce81384e32f18b6f5fa43", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:16", "text": "并选择"}
{"id": "533d0b5212accce01358338ee9290a8d7fde3f7d920074e3ef190ced16538122", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:17", "text": "Fast point instancing（快速点实例化）"}
{"id": "7175517a370b5cd2e664e3fd29c4ea9db5ce17058eb9772fe090a5485e49dad6", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:18", "text": "或"}
{"id": "0aea4dda658e123ee4842e1b457a9696b915d1ddc5662dfe1c9d497d98ee8d4a", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:19", "text": "Full point instancing（完整点实例化）"}
{"id": "9fdcb81f4ad021e426f4bb2610e92bc1eb9d83cf7d41c5d6c3e4aaa967c8d341", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:20", "text": "。目前这两个选项在渲染器中会产生相同的行为。"}
{"id": "fa3838a23e4828b0b4e634bdea27002f49030342ff706d155976d1ed70c75254", "item_id": "ecf6aa9273:21", "text": "若要覆盖实例化对象的材质，可以在 Instance 内部使用 Material SOP。"}
